Keep the Dockerfile in a empty directory.

Build the container - $ sudo docker build -t <tag-name> .

start the container - $ sudo docker run -it -p 8888:8888 <image-id>

Execute the command inside the container - $ pyspark

open your favourite browser - localhost:8888


To list images - sudo docker images

To list running containers - sudo docker ps

To copy data from local host to docker container - sudo docker cp LOCALPATH CONTAINER ID:PATH

To copy data from docker container to local host - sudo docker cp CONTAINER ID:PATH LOCALPATH

To commit chages in docker container - sudo docker commit container ID tag-name:version
